    "summary": "This copybook defines the data structure COPAU1AI, which is used for screen input and output. It contains fields for transaction name, titles, current date and time, card number, authorization details, POS entry mode, authorization source, MCC code, card expiry date, authorization type, transaction ID, authorization match, authorization forward, merchant name, merchant ID, merchant city, merchant state, merchant zip code, and error message. It also redefines COPAU1AI as COPAU1AO to provide individual character access to the same fields.",
